    dc:description "FIGURES 1−13. Pipunculus caeruleus sp. nov. (CEUA-101617). Holotype male. 1, Habitus, left lateral view; 2, Habitus, dorsal view; 3, Antenna; 4, Thorax, dorsal view; 5, Wing; 6, Abdomen, dorsal view; 7, Tergites and sternites 6 and 7, ventral view; 8, Terminalia, dorsal view; 9, Left surstylus, lateral view; 10, Right surstylus, lateral view; 11, Hypandrium and gonopods, ventral view, 12, Phallic guide and phallus, left lateral view; 13, Ejaculatory apodeme." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10417474/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

